Lindblad operators b1, b2, ... into an ordinary differential equation for the \
column vector consisting of the components of the density operator in the \
so-called Lie basis. LindbladConvert[cm] assumes that Choi matrix cm \
corresponds to the Lindblad generator.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, 
